<li class="toclevel-2 tocsection-5"><a href="#England_v_Germany_at_the_2010_World_Cup"><span class="tocnumber">3.2</span> <span class="toctext">England v Germany at the 2010 World Cup</span></a></li>
<li class="toclevel-2 tocsection-6"><a href="#England_v_Ukraine_at_Euro_2012"><span class="tocnumber">3.3</span> <span class="toctext">England v Ukraine at Euro 2012</span></a></li>
</ul>
</li>
